\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 These feats of markmanship are in the true mike fink tradition, which ranged from driving nails with bullets to shooting tin cups and scalp locks from heatds. Most of his shooting wagers were sadistic pranks\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85unlike the former rascals who thought that \u8220\'93even a crime might take on the aspect of a good joke,\u8221\'94 Mike was one to carry a joke to the point of being a crime. ; shooting off a negros heel because he disliked it\u8217\'92s shape., forcing his woman to lie down I na pile of leaves to which he set fire, to cure her of looking at other men.}
